description: I've created guides for the future cybercriminal and hacker out there looking for a helping hand into the hacking world. These are designed in a way so you learn all the skills on how to target an individual or company and compromise their computer with all open source and free tools while remaining anonymous. These guides are catered to individuals with little to no programming skills. The beginner/intermediate hacker will benefit greatly from these!
name: HackTown
